Package: UndercountR
Title: Bayesian Modeling for Underreported Count Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Theophilus", "Anim Bediako", , "theophilus.animbediako@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for modeling underreported count data using Bayesian inference. 
    Supports Poisson, Negative Binomial, and Zero-Inflated models with optional validation data.
